ornell——并说他“几乎要加入他们的行列”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/disturbeds-david-draiman-reunited-with-missing-family-puppy-3508220">《Disturbed》的 David Draiman 与失踪的家庭小狗团聚的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Lil Tay 公开谈论死亡骗局并推出新单曲《Sucker 4 Green》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-tay-opens-up-about-death-hoax-and-drops-new-track-sucker-4-green-3508229?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=小泰打开了关于死亡骗局并掉落了新轨道吸盘 4 绿色Liberty DunworthTue, 03 Oct 2023 08:41:46 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3508229 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “你们这些婊子都以为演出结束了”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-tay-opens-up-about-death-hoax-and-drops-new-track-sucker-4-green-3508229">Lil Tay 的帖子公开了死亡骗局，并放弃了新单曲“Sucker 4 Green”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在她涉嫌死亡的消息传开近两个月后，14 岁的说唱歌手 Lil Tay 公开揭露了这一骗局，并推出了一首新单曲“Sucker 4 Green”。</p><p>关于这位音乐家去世的谣言早在 8 月份就已传开，当时据<em><a href="https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/701800-lil-tay-dead-at-14" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《Hot New Hip Hop》</a></em>报道，这位青春期病毒明星去世时年仅 14 岁。</p><p> “我们怀着沉重的心情分享我们挚爱的克莱尔突然悲惨去世的毁灭性消息，”她家人的留言中写道。 “我们无法用言语来表达无法承受的损失和难以形容的痛苦。”</p><p>声明还称，Lil Tay 的哥哥 Jason Tian 也去世了，并补充说，两起死亡事件“仍在调查中”。</p><p>该消息后来从 Instagram 上删除， <em><a href="https://www.tmz.com/2023/08/10/lil-tay-social-media-star-still-alive-instagram-hacked-fake-death-hoax/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TMZ</a></em>随后报道称 Lil Tay 和她的兄弟还活着，而她的社交媒体帐户已被黑客入侵。 “我想明确表示，我和我的兄弟都安全还活着，但我完全心碎，甚至很难找到合适的词语来表达，”她告诉媒体。</p><p>现在，这位说唱歌手公开了这一骗局，并通过推出新单曲让她重返音乐界。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cx06OeCPZji/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="non